7">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11000074/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=A+retrospective+comparison+of+abdominal+muscle+strength+following+breast+reconstruction+with+a+free+TRAM+or+DIEP+flap&amp;author=CM+Futter&amp;author=MH+Webster&amp;author=S+Hagen&amp;author=SL+Mitchell&amp;publication_year=2000&amp;journal=Br+J+Plast+Surg&amp;pages=578-583&amp;doi=10.1054%2Fbjps.2000.3427&amp;pmid=11000074">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">18.</div><div id="r18" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Chen CM, Halvorson EG, Disa JJ, et al. Immediate postoperative complications in DIEP versus free/muscle-sparing TRAM flaps. <em>Plast Reconstr Surg</em> 2007;120(6):1477–1482.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1097/01.prs.0000288014.76151.f7">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18040176/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Immediate+postoperative+complications+in+DIEP+versus+free%2Fmuscle-sparing+TRAM+flaps&amp;author=CM+Chen&amp;author=EG+Halvorson&amp;author=JJ+Disa&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;journal=Plast+Reconstr+Surg&amp;pages=1477-1482&amp;doi=10.1097%2F01.prs.0000288014.76151.f7&amp;pmid=18040176">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">19.</div><div id="r19" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Grotting JC. The free abdominoplasty flap for immediate breast reconstruction. <em>Ann Plast Surg</em> 1991;27(4):351–354.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1097/00000637-199110000-00011">Crossre